---
// Encart promotionnel pour la page Facebook
---

<div
  class="lg:hidden relative bg-gradient-to-br from-container to-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg border-2 border-[#1877f2]/50 overflow-hidden mb-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
>
  <div
    class="p-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center text-center md:text-left space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-6"
  >
    <!-- Icône Facebook -->
    <div
      class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#1877f2] text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg flex-shrink-0"
    >
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8">
        <path
          d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"
        ></path>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <!-- Contenu textuel -->
    <div class="space-y-3 flex-1">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[--color-text-primary]">
        Suivez-nous sur Facebook !
      </h3>
      <p
        class="text-sm text-[--color-text-primary] opacity-80 leading-relaxed max-w-md"
      >
        Rejoignez notre communauté des Disciples d'Escoffier Provence
        Méditerranée et découvrez nos actualités, événements et initiatives
        culinaires.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bouton d'action -->
    <a
      href="https://www.facebook.com/disciples.escoffier.provence.mediterranee"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2 bg-[#1877f2] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md"
    >
      Nous suivre
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
